pages.text: The End Mechanic Soul is turtle upgrade, that transform turtle into end-kind automata!$(p)This upgrade allow everything, that $(l:items/weak_mechanic_soul)Weak mechanic soul$() does and also provide ability to teleport to stored positions by marks!$(p)For the full documentation please see the $(9)$(l:https://docs.srendi.de/items/end_mechanic_soul/)official wiki page$(/l)$()!
